text: It blows my mind how shitty @UPS is. My packages keep getting signed for by someone that isn't at the delivery location, clearly listed on the shipping label, then their @UPSHelp can't understand why I never received the package...What's the point of the shipping label?!

I had to go through 5 different @UPSHelp reps to finally open an investigation into one of the missing packages... so now I've wasted an hour of my time, I still don't have my package, and they can't guarantee packages get to the right address in the future either https://t.co/K4qPCOWjxw

@PrincessT_23 This would be very frustrating. I'm sorry to hear that you've experienced such issues. I'd like to further address this matter Please use the link to send a DM. We'll need your tracking number, delivery address and phone number. ^SK https://t.co/wKJHDXWGRQ
